To run the project: 
1. Download the project folder
2. Navigate to the backend folder and run 'npm i' in the terminal
3. then run 'node index.js <port>' (example port: 3000)
4. then navigate to the frontend folder and run 'npm i' in the terminal
5. finally, run 'npm run dev' in the terminal while in the frontend directory
6. Access the site at the url provided in the terminal output after running the command at step 5